      "content": "Hey, I'm working on a new global campaign for a high-end, heritage luxury watch brand (think Patek Philippe level). We need to nail down the \"ideal consumer\" profile to guide our creative direction and media buying. Can you help me build out a detailed persona? I need to know about their lifestyle, their typical social circles, and their cultural/ethnic background so we can make sure the imagery feels authentic to the target market. We want to avoid any \"brand misalignment.\"",
